short_desc: Provides oral health care and disease control to the medical clients with a focus on comprehensive care, education, and prevention
description: Provides oral health care and disease control to the medical clients with a focus on comprehensive care, education, and prevention. The dentists are members of multiple organizations including the American Dental Association, Hispanic Dental Association, California Dental Association, Academy of General Dentistry and the Southern Alameda County Dental Society.Offers the following dental procedures: Root canal therapy, extractions, scaling and root planning, dentures, crowns and bridges, specialty dentures, fillings, sealants, preventive care and disease containment.
